The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Sunday, June 26, 2005 

 Hesperus best bet for Million 

 WILLIAM TELL

 Bangalore: The 1,200m Juvenile Sprinters Million, a terms race for youngsters which is the main attraction here on Sunday, appears to be a straight contest between Hesperus and Diomedes. However, the Darius Byramji-trained Hesperus, with K. P. Appu in the saddle, is tipped to win the trophy.

